t fils.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Dialogue+aux+enfers+entre+Machiavel+et+Montesquieu+ou+la+politique+de+Machiavel+au+XIX%3Csup%3Ee%3C%2Fsup%3E+si%C3%A8cle&amp;rft.place=Bruxelles&amp;rft.pub=A.+Mertens+et+fils&amp;rft.date=1864&amp;rft.au=Maurice+Joly&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Ffr.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FDialogue_aux_enfers_entre_Machiavel_et_Montesquieu&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Dialogue+in+Hell+Between+Machiavelli+and+Montesquieu\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation book\">Maurice Joly (1868). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k5427027b\"><i>Dialogue aux Enfers entre Machiavel et Montesquieu, ou la Politique au XIXe si\u00e8cle, par un contemporain &#91;Maurice Joly&#93;</i></a>. Bruxelles: Tous les libraires.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Dialogue+aux+Enfers+entre+Machiavel+et+Montesquieu%2C+ou+la+Politique+au+XIXe+si%C3%A8cle%2C+par+un+contemporain+%5BMaurice+Joly%5D&amp;rft.place=Bruxelles&amp;rft.pub=Tous+les+libraires&amp;rft.date=1868&amp;rft.au=Maurice+Joly&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fgallica.bnf.fr%2Fark%3A%2F12148%2Fbpt6k5427027b&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Dialogue+in+Hell+Between+Machiavelli+and+Montesquieu\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation journal\">Maurice Joly (30 April 1870). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k519820